content.rendered:
The gate of time opens for a legendary swordsman who wants to obtain the sword of divine power at the twilight of the Goryeo dynasty. On the other side of the gate, however, are those who are chasing an alien prisoner locked in a human body in 2022.

Directed By Dong-hoon Choi

Written By Dong-hoon Choi

Stars: Kim Eui-sung. Lee Hanee. Yoo Jae-myung
